Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.20,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\bord6.75\pos(1356.226,924.75)\i1\3c&H67D9C7&\blur2.25}Mai là tới nghỉ hè
